metadata.title: Thorsen's Greenhouse Marble Queen Pothos, Live Indoor Plant, 4" Diameter Pot, Classic Pot Cover (White)
description: Marble Queen Pothos has beautiful white and green variegated leaves! This houseplant is popular for new plant parents, due to the forgiving nature and low-maintenance requirements for care. Marble Queen Pothos plants look beautiful trailing down a windowsill, bookshelf, or even in a hanging planter!
